collectors.title: Database
collectors.titleDetails: (3 total Queries, 3 of them unique across 1 Connection)

queries.sql:
select wpID,wp.added_by,wp.client, wp.auditor, wp.supervisor,wp.audmanager, wp.firm,wp.jobdur,wp.financial_year,wp.end_financial_year,wp.status,wp.remarks,wp.added_on,
        (select name from tbl_users as tu where tu.userID = wp.auditor) as aud,
        (select name from tbl_users as tu where tu.userID = wp.supervisor) as sup,
        (select name from tbl_users as tu where tu.userID = wp.audmanager) as audm,
        (select signature from tbl_users as tu where tu.userID = wp.auditor) as audsign,
        (select signature from tbl_users as tu where tu.userID = wp.supervisor) as supsign,
        (select signature from tbl_users as tu where tu.userID = wp.audmanager) as mansign,
        tc.name as clientname
        from tbl_workpaper as wp, tbl_clients as tc
        where tc.cID = wp.client
        and wp.wpID = 4
        and wp.client = 5

select distinct prepared_on,reviewed_on,approved_on 
        from tbl_client_files_c3 as c3 
        where c3.workpaper = 4
        and c3.clientID = 5
        and c3.c3tID = 54 limit 1
